217
00:18:48,140 --> 00:18:50,000
- Alô?
- Bob?

218
00:18:50,000 --> 00:18:51,630
Anh còn đấy không?

219
00:18:51,630 --> 00:18:55,570
Thôi nào, nghe tôi đi. Bob!

220
00:18:58,660 --> 00:18:59,780
Bob!

221
00:19:07,380 --> 00:19:08,780
Thôi đi!

